messages.message:
-------------
Resposting here, since its an eng wide change:

As next steps on the proposal (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1WYd-Ozvw1AmloiIvbqwyP6h06KF2a1NF2V5UgUmawP0/edit# ), we are adding `flake8` pre-commit hook.

The PR for this change is here: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/11054

The PR is approved and I plan to merge it at 10 am tomorrow. If you have any concerns, please reach out to me before then.

For your convenience, the following `two short videos` show the process of committing your changes when this hook is enabled.
1. `Standard user-flow`:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1mbDBHlMDvEm0A13cReEAgDpeJ5uUFfiY/view

2.`In case of emergencies, when you absolutely need to skip the hook`:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1crzGatvC5b4N3fJq_KczdFWyu4cmEwZ6/view
